N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 28.4 - Filing reports

State Regulations

Each holder of a permit issued hereunder shall make and
file with the State Liquor Authority such reports as shall be required by the

State Liquor Authority. Notes
